{"tid":363683,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"［有感］啱啱終於睇完末日時在做什麼","createTime":"2017-08-17T20:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T13:07:27.000Z","uid":102208,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fabdce9f1acd7c367da2f888219eab24cfb12ec8","tid":363683,"uid":102208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T20:46:09.000Z","msg":"套野真係好好睇 好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但好睇感動嘅原因係完全唔關女主事<br />\n而係因為蓮<br />\n<br />\n先唔講第十一二集嘅時候<br />\n蓮嘅種種付出行為<br />\n由男主第一日返工嘅時候<br />\n蓮已經洞悉到男主嘅狀況<br />\n仲一路陪著男主比安慰佢<br />\n正係依點已經令佢超哂女主班<br />\n<br />\n到到12集嘅依一幕<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/18/042205_f53f397888856382e07b00c5bb8795c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F18%2F042205_f53f397888856382e07b00c5bb8795c4.jpg&h=619e1baa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男主抱住佢一齊跌落去個一段<br />\n真係睇到我流哂馬尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到連女主係咁比食人花係咁插插我都覺得無所謂了<br />\n到到最後見到蓮張黑白照<br />\n我嘅心情到依家都仲未平復到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總括而言<br />\n我覺得蓮先係真正嘅女主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好耐未試過睇一套野覺得主角魅力唔夠其他角色勁<br />\n唔知有無ching同我一樣諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申：訓住打依篇野，如果有啲咩錯記得屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"01c220cbb0ceccf3c103d916ddbf948174945095","tid":363683,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T21:08:42.000Z","msg":"去睇埋小說 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37431b594be70b095ca58dcc20c1e5e94228d6a4","tid":363683,"uid":102208,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T03:36:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去睇埋小說 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱啱睇左少少小説劇透<br />\n總算係放下心頭大石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a81be053a08b57ef51935805584ee640a52e737","tid":363683,"uid":46389,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T03:54:13.000Z","msg":"珂朵莉女子力超曬班"},{"pid":"b853ceb6f9a35b9cf7e97cfa0a9c1e2cc1f5a080","tid":363683,"uid":102208,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T07:35:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>珂朵莉女子力超曬班</blockquote><br />\n你指能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f85f5e02e968d93e485471a13a7cd00030a24ff","tid":363683,"uid":22663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T07:55:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />頭尾兩段Scarborough fair呼應感動啲"},{"pid":"f020c304c8de98e4bc53501c5ddeb0d0a51f6c95","tid":363683,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T09:33:16.000Z","msg":"蓮真係個好女仔黎"},{"pid":"8178832a2a60c87722b7998e94a2d2584bae6a82","tid":363683,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T10:38:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蓮真係個好女仔黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07aa3c17f0f0d6934d5db1098f3af33a856c4860","tid":363683,"uid":49995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T10:50:39.000Z","msg":"可惜第四卷蓮既回合動畫未做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"922b0ab40e2c69fa08ebc67bc862af250f32a14d","tid":363683,"uid":102208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T11:57:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>蓮真係個好女仔黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱呀Ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659cf573a375dc0aefc13d3d5cc3edf9d575fa9e","tid":363683,"uid":102208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T11:59:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可惜第四卷蓮既回合動畫未做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好想快啲睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d00b8765b10290dc214843692bad995a34633e","tid":363683,"uid":8291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T12:08:16.000Z","msg":"第十二集蓮比獸打到起唔番身 隻手抽曬筋<br />\n但係為左完成黃金妖精既職責<br />\n蓮都夾硬起番身去戰鬥<br />\n<br />\n呢一幕真係睇到起曬雞皮"},{"pid":"888c60e8ca8d9e13074125ea668f29feabb76b78","tid":363683,"uid":102208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T12:43:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第十二集蓮比獸打到起唔番身 隻手抽曬筋<br />\n但係為左完成黃金妖精既職責<br />\n蓮都夾硬起番身去戰鬥<br />\n<br />\n呢一幕真係睇到起曬雞皮</blockquote><br />\n仲有呢一幕<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201706/bfdbf8f11e9c11a47911cf4e3fc179f5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201706%2Fbfdbf8f11e9c11a47911cf4e3fc179f5.JPG&h=4b76f348&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本來無咩表情嘅佢都露出咁嘅笑容<br />\n見到佢依個表情同跌落去真係好心酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53997c0f8a8568c3c215d376fea9f5baa1f2b0a6","tid":363683,"uid":102208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T03:14:43.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3acd49851f596c1cd6d16baee3c1a76a81c2e2e","tid":363683,"uid":6193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T03:19:52.000Z","msg":"會唔會第2季講埋後續 正式完第一部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8ce9787996018